Use Source Report Charts in Dashboard Widgets

Youâ€™ve already charted data just the way you like in a report. Instead of re-creating the chart, use it in a dashboard widget.

To create dashboards: Run Reports AND Create and Customize Dashboards
To edit and delete dashboards that you created: Run Reports AND Create and Customize Dashboards
To edit and delete dashboards that you created in public folders: Edit My Dashboards
Create or edit a dashboard. Click + Widget and select Chart or Table, or edit an existing one by clicking  on the widget.
From the Add Component or Edit Component menu, select Use chart settings from report.

The dashboard widget displays the source report chart. To customize the chart, deselect Use chart settings from report or edit the report chart.
title: Using Report Charts in Salesforce Dashboards
